      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and user qualification records consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2022R2 is used under an ISO 9001-registered QMS. Version control logs, regression test suite results, and analyst qualification certificates are on file. All SQA requirements for MRL 2 are satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
