      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via benchmark problems with known analytical solutions at MRL 2 level.",
      "rationale": "Fluent v2022R2 code verification benchmarks (lid-driven cavity, Poiseuille flow, rotating disk) confirm correct implementation of the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations. Published verification reports from ANSYS accompany the submission."
    },
