      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for shear stress QoI must be below 5% on the production mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the FDA pump geometry. GCI for volume-averaged shear stress is 2.8% on the production mesh (12.4 M cells), satisfying the 5% acceptance criterion. Richardson extrapolation confirms monotonic convergence."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
