      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation must be documented with uncertainty bounds and must correspond to at least 3 of the 5 simulated operating points.",
      "rationale": "In vitro bench tests were conducted at all 5 flow-speed operating points (2, 3, 4, 5, 6 L/min at 2500 RPM) in a temperature-controlled loop using bovine blood with documented hematocrit (35±2%). Test conditions are fully documented with calibration records for flow meters and pressure transducers."
