      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the identical FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used in the COU. Bovine blood rheology is within accepted equivalence bounds for human blood at CPB hematocrits. Operating points span the full clinical flow range (2–6 L/min), confirming validation coverage of the COU envelope."
    },
