      "rationale": "Solver residuals for continuity, momentum, and turbulence equations converge to 1e-5 or better for all simulations. Explicit propagation of solver error to QoI uncertainty is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed; default convergence criteria are deemed sufficient."
