      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, systematic review of user-introduced errors beyond standard peer review of simulation setup is not required.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup was independently peer-reviewed by a second qualified CFD analyst. Formal use-error analysis (e.g., FMEA of user inputs) is not required at MRL 2 and has not been conducted. Peer review records are archived."
    },
    {
