      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required; selection of turbulence and hemolysis models must be documented and justified.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model and Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model were selected based on published literature for rotating blood-contacting devices. Model form uncertainty quantification beyond this literature justification is not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
