      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, probabilistic sensitivity analysis of model input parameters is not required; nominal input values must be documented with sources.",
      "rationale": "All model inputs (viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients, boundary conditions) are documented with literature or measurement sources. Probabilistic input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed."
